$t[2] = 'Shĩ ne wanda Ya fitar da waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta daga Maz&otilde;wa Litt&atilde;fi, daga gid&atilde;jẽnsu da k&otilde;ra ta farko. Ba ku yi zaton sun&atilde; fita ba, kuma sun tabbata cẽwa g&atilde;nuw&otilde;winsu m&atilde;su tsare su ne daga Allah, sai Allah Ya jẽ musu daga wajen da ba su yi zato ba, kuma Ya jẽfa ts&otilde;ro a cikin zuk&atilde;tansu, sun&atilde; rushe gid&atilde;jensu da hann&atilde;yensu da kuma hann&atilde;yen mũminai. To, ku lũra fa, ya m&atilde;su basĩr&otilde;ri.';
$t[3] = 'Kuma ba d&otilde;min Allah Ya rubuta musu k&otilde;rar ba, d&atilde; Ya azabta su a cikin dũniya, kuma a L&atilde;hira sun&atilde; da az&atilde;bar wut&atilde;.';
$t[4] = 'Wannan d&otilde;min lalle su, sun s&atilde;ɓa wa Allah, da ManzonSa alh&atilde;li kuwa wanda ya s&atilde;ɓa wa Allah, to, lalle Allah, Mai tsananin uƙũba ne.';
$t[5] = 'Abin da kuka s&atilde;re na dabĩniya, k&otilde; kuka bar ta tsaye a kan asallanta, to da iznin Allah ne, kuma d&otilde;min Ya wul&atilde;kanta fasiƙai,';
